{"tid":388170,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"識唔識d人幾個月轉一次工，但係次次都加人工","createTime":"2017-09-05T09:14:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T09:41:55.000Z","uid":60527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"28b7f067d1ccfade572ddd7383952d2104ffa64e","tid":388170,"uid":60527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T09:14:49.000Z","msg":"有幾個fd都係咁<br />\n唔係專業人仕，普通degree仔(即係bba,ss之類)，唔係sales，只係私人公司文職<br />\n我見佢地幾個月至一年就轉一次工，每次都係裸辭，辭完1個禮拜左右就有新offer<br />\n重要每次轉完工都加幾千蚊人工，依家grad左幾年已經逗緊fg果陣幾倍人工<br />\n其實私人公司常唔常見嫁，定係佢地幾個真係好出色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我問佢地，佢地只係話其實唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fead68834d445ba5dfab9349249ec9bb80afec45","tid":388170,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T09:18:20.000Z","msg":"人勁做咩都賺到錢架啦"},{"pid":"2f31ccc69633bc33e7ef93145017d91c292f9a5c","tid":388170,"uid":60527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T09:20:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人勁做咩都賺到錢架啦</blockquote><br />\n就係唔知行情先問下出面私人公司咁樣常唔常見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3d61729eced5e386082837d2563e042c52c8c0d","tid":388170,"uid":92381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T09:21:16.000Z","msg":"咩職級先"},{"pid":"003d15fd7cb7cb6a454e8a52714dd26acf71d689","tid":388170,"uid":136645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T09:22:45.000Z","msg":"文職都咁高人工"},{"pid":"aed8473985408961a9309d69fe81fff826735e3d","tid":388170,"uid":59192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T09:23:00.000Z","msg":"咩u"},{"pid":"4d810ddaf665d4e06f140986c4401a2ab5cb3fd5","tid":388170,"uid":45301,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T09:24:35.000Z","msg":"Fg當萬五<br />\n幾倍當3倍<br />\nGrad左幾年月入就45000？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8abd447bb22f39373d4b5f1b